End Function


'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
'   IComparer
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
Private Function IComparer_Compare(a As Variant, b As Variant) As Long
    IComparer_Compare = Compare(a, b)
End Function
